        <member name="T:HdmtOs.Sdk.TestClass.BaseTypes.Attributes.TestClassLoaderAttribute">
             <summary>
             Specifies the TestClassLoader for the HdmtOsTestClass
             </summary>
             <remarks>
             The TestProgramHost will instantiate the TestClassLoader instead of the class
             this attribute is specified on.
            
             The TestContext.TestInformation.LoadDll will reference the loadDll
             
             The TestClassLoader will be responsible for instantiating the HdmtOsTestClass
             </remarks>
        </member>
